Available Tools: process_cash | process_card | process_mobile_pay | get_change | refund_transaction
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "amount": number, "currency": "string", "transaction_id": "string" }
Response Schema: { "transaction_id": "string", "status": "string", "change": number, "receipt": "string" }
---
Question: A customer inserts a $20 bill to buy a soda priced at $1.75.
Call: { "func_call": "process_cash", "amount": 20.00, "currency": "USD", "transaction_id": "VM-2023-8841" }
Response: { "transaction_id": "VM-2023-8841", "status": "success", "change": 18.25, "receipt": "RCP-8841-A1" }

Question: Someone pays $3.50 using a credit card for a bag of chips.
